text: Yekaterina Zhdanova born ) is a Kazakhstani female volleyball player. She is a member of the Kazakhstan women's national volleyball team and played for Zhetyssu in 2011. She was part of the Kazakhstani national team at the 2011 FIVB World Grand Prix in Italy, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2017 FIVB World Grand Prix. == Clubs == * Zhetyssu (2011) == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * http://www.zimbio.com/photos/Yekaterina+Zhdanova/19th+Asian+Senior+Women+Volleyball+Championship/6jcHx6kEIMs * http://www.bta.bg/en/gallery/image/5146388 * http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-08/11/c_136517749.htm Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Volleyball players at the 2018 Asian Games
